Kevin Sorbo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Sorbo 0 Kevin David Sorbo (born September 24, 1958) is an American actor. He is best known for his starring roles in two television series: as Hercules in Hercules: The Legendary Journeys, and as Captain Dylan Hunt in Andromeda.
